The paper discusses data summarization techniques for scientific simulations, which involves analyzing and visualizing multiple variables together. This suggests that the paper may belong to the Graphics (cs.GR) or Databases (cs.DB) sub-categories. The proposed algorithm also uses statistical measures to quantify the association between data points, which suggests that it may belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) or Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Finally, the paper also discusses visualization techniques, which suggests that it may belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category.
